[l] Erbauliches aus FBI-Abhoeraktionen:In 2013, a Russian intelligence operative who was posing as a United Nations diplomat met Page at an Asia Society conference; according to the F.B.I., the Russian spy tried to recruit Page but encountered difficulties because, as he was heard telling a colleague in an F.B.I. wiretap, Page was “an idiot.”Das muss schon hart sein, wenn die Russen es nicht uebers Herz bringen, dich zu rekrutieren, weil sie dich fuer zu bloede halten.
